These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, colonial
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, january
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, green
1. the tower house is on the far right##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| House       | colonial       | tower |
| Birthday         | january | april  |
| Cigar       | blend    | bongani    |
| Color   | green       | chestnut      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
2 different pets are kept: snake, fish
There 2 different types of food: kale, pineapple
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games
1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Birthday      | october     | may |
| Pet           | snake | fish      |
| Food   | pineapple  | kale      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | board-games     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, writer
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, russian
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia
1. the russian is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the security-guard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Flower      | aconite | sunflower  |
| Job          | security-guard    | writer   |
| Nationality   | russian  | japanese   |
| Color     | fuchsia     | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different pets are kept: horse, ferret
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Pet      | horse       | ferret |
| Nationality          | brazilian         | egyptian    |
| Flower           | marigold | azalea    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey           | soccer   |

