There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, aquamarine
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, punk
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the brazilian is the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the nigerian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| City         | nizza            | venice  |
| Color           | aquamarine | light-blue |
| Nationality   | nigerian           | brazilian       |
| Music-Genre     | techno            | punk        |

