.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, drama
2 different games are played: snooker, domino
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire         | drama    |
| Game       | domino     | snooker  |
| Cigar      | oliveros | vegafina     |
| Sport        | badminton     | snowboarding |

