.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
City: san-francisco, paris
House: farmhouse, ranch-style
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, russian
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, skydiving
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the colombian is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| City           | paris | san-francisco     |
| House   | farmhouse          | ranch-style |
| Nationality           | colombian          | russian    |
| Hobby     | skydiving            | writing       |

 